You're really dedicated, I appreciate that in a person!
You have been awarded the title of Dedicated!
Oh, I could always use more pieces...
Hey! Maybe if you bring me enough I could come up with a little something special for ya, ya know?
Oh, I see you're here for Marcus's latest requests.
One is used to open rifts. It's a crazy sight to behold... you'll be ripped directly into the rift.
The other is used to close rifts once you are inside. I can't truly say what that's like...
Beautiful piece of work isn't she?
Kaywin looks at the machine quizzically.
No matter how many time I fix her she just seems to keep breaking down.
A friend of mine found that list, it's full of wonderful things I could use. With my skills and those parts I could keep her running indefinitely.
How am I supposed to fix this with nothing but naught? Maybe I'll get a few more pieces of alloy today... that'd be so great!
